Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.20,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be1\an8}翻译：萝卜子；校对：千葉命；歌词：七海·拓；\N后期：消失的风使；繁化：黑羽侖人。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢藤冈什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起  圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题太突然  我有点儿手足无措 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…太突然了点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问喜欢什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…那是我们开学典礼那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  一时半会是完不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是忘了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值日生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我突然感到乏力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事儿吧  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能没事儿啊  剩下的就拜托各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:43.83,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第11碗  果然不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫弗拉思科还是叫弗朗西斯科的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp5}　{\fsp1}Elastico{\r}\N是牛尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  叫什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp1}Elastico{\fsp485}　{\fsp1}{\r}\N牛尾巴呢  是南美某个足球运动员常用的假动作的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  身体怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经好了  没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊  难得你过来了  进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…藤冈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子制服啊  真可爱  真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先换上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看藤冈那反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计误认为你因某种理由穿了千秋的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  没穿帮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp33}　{\fsp1}churrasco{\fsp1}{\fsp13}　{\fsp1}Elastico{\r}\N还能和藤冈讨论巴西烧烤和牛尾巴的共同点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是什么玩意  我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会编出个你穿女子制服的理由帮你过关的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  夏奈她们在里屋干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  藤冈  你也别反抗了  穿上这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是让客人穿奇装异服博我开心的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没听说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也行  好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学学冬马啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话了  赶紧穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我穿不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  绝对不要  放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这睡觉会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  明天是清扫街道的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实今天早上就有点儿发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看果然是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你睡被炉里的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  赶紧上床休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿我熬粥给你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…我看是没法去清扫街道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  其实我也想陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过又不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让千秋陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么需要不用客气跟她说就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事  就摇这个铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午左右就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了对了  你还是只能吃些清淡的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？啊  都能吃都能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想  多吃才恢复得快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那午饭想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你做些喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天这么冷  砂锅面应该不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿果汁来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我有点儿渴了  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么能喝的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看完了  下一本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（东家三姐妹）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样了  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去做饭  等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:10:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂锅面到底是煮出来的还是烧出来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话了  赶紧拿过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气喽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在装病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊  怀疑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这亲姐姐说的话你都不信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要给你量个体温
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我去拿温度计来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样才量得准
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过不想去扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就装病骗我和春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事儿  我是真的…感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要睡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是星期天  就让我多睡会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了今天的安排了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不带你了啊  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  今天白天要去买春装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上可以吃烤五花肉自助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有股可怕的寒意袭来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能料到事情会发展到如此不可预料的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是说我感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道千秋又要说些什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说买东西  我很想吃五花肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得烤五花肉自助是有期限的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错过这次机会就不知道下次是什么时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想点办法的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她该在准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  不快点儿换衣服就不带你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我还有很多作业要写
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…为了晚上能痛痛快快的吃自助  得先写完作业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见啊  夏奈竟会担心作业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…这个嘛  偶尔也该认真的写一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我也想安心地吃五花肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…买东西就
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就拜托春香和千秋你们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我会在晚饭前写完作业的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西就拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西的问题总算解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就是在晚饭前治好感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾  我还想难得能三人一起逛逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来买东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学是运动会的执行委员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回头学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  没人在吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是夏奈叫我帮她买东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门开着…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！被炉里有个镐形头盔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（镐形头盔：竖于头盔钱的一种装饰，像角一样高高伸向左右两边） 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…是内田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都窝在被炉里…一不注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡被炉更不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡去床上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…那个…糟糕的是我昨天感冒过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在装病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过不想去扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就装病骗我和春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事儿才刚完  今天不能再说感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  内田  我感冒的事谁也别告诉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:04.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}（※同时服用多种药物时需谨慎）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你说的都拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你们我补充了足够的营养
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  内田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我房间把毛毯拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护嗓子需要的就是湿度  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从厨房拿热水来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就OK了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着把被炉的温度调到最高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样感冒能好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  要在床上好好休息才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行  不知道春香她们什么时候回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须时刻准备着恢复平常的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要的是毅力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅力…毅力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买到合适的真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给夏奈买了可爱的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真期待五花肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要奢侈一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望夏奈作业也写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她肯定写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…越来越难受了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再跟千秋说我感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她会怎么骂我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要装得跟平常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常是什么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先全身放松
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般会躺着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就会想钻进被炉里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只镐形头盔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  不是说了在被炉里睡觉会感冒的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会感冒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音好像很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…在头盔里钻太久…嗓子干了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话的方式也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…在头盔里钻太久…被热晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在桌炉里钻太久  就这么睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  没事的  休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大人  千秋大人在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想近期跟藤冈做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平且和睦地了断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不明原委
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是吵头儿头儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也差不多觉得烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈在你和春香面前不会显露出他本来面目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其中就包含和他搞好关系的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真有一天能表明爱意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该感到厌烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你要怎么了断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就教你一招关系恶化时的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终奥义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  最好是用不上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么叫春香和千秋就用名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却只叫我姓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家里都是姓南的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就叫我「小夏奈」吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…不好意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  惹他生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背摔啊！摔不动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  你教的奥义毫无用处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系倒是没恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他问我「你干什么啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真照做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得刮过胡子后反而变得更浓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刮过之后会看到比较粗的根部  可能会有这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是在毛长出来的时候会觉得全体截面面积变大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从医学上来讲  胡子的量和其本身并没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以安心的刮掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:44.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(250,0)}第12碗  「一口也吃不下了」
